\section{Conclusion}
We presented \textbf{RAG AI Scientist} alongside a public evaluation protocol and used an ATLAS Higgs-challenge replication as a validation testbed. The evaluation harness is designed to expose corpus-coverage gaps rather than paper over them, so even a failing run produces a concrete artifact (the failure-case table) guiding corpus maintenance. Code, configuration, and this document regenerate from a single command.

